{
  "stem": "17761.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 130.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- her ancestors-- I don't know exactly to which generation to go back-- were the founders of that community in this village.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First of all, my mother was the most loyal human being that you can imagine to her family, to her children.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And just to illustrate this, my father's father in his latest years of life lived in our-- in our house.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had some special condition to be treated.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she-- it was not always pleasant to do that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She did it until the last of his days, to the extent that for years my father and my mother could never go out somewhere together.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Always one had to stay with my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She did it full-heartedly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I never heard any complaint about this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she was just a very good human being.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So because I'm talking now about my mother, I'll start from the grandparents of my mother.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Excuse me, please.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[DRINKS] As most of the Jews in that village and the villages around, he had also a shop, where he was selling all kinds of things, like wheat and sugar and flour and all kind of these things to the people living in that village.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he had also some fields outside of the village where I like to go with one of his daughters who used to drive the horses there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we used to collect the-- the what has grown on the fields and to come back on a high wagon full with all this stuff.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they had also cows in-- in the courtyard, so we had fresh milk.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My grandmother used to-- to make butter out of the milk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she was a very good cook, so all these kinds are together in my picture from this little village.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
